WEBVTT

00:05:28.390 --> 00:05:30.119
I'd like you to unlock your phone.

00:05:33.807 --> 00:05:37.624
Now hand your unlocked phone
to the person on your left.

00:05:37.648 --> 00:05:41.353
(Laughter)

00:05:49.734 --> 00:05:52.547
That tiny sense of panic
you're feeling right now --

00:05:52.571 --> 00:05:54.246
(Laughter)

00:05:54.270 --> 00:05:57.600
is exactly how hosts feel the first time
they open their home.

00:05:58.581 --> 00:06:01.338
Because the only thing
more personal than your phone